177 A.3d 129 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. M.E.D., DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C—447 September Term 2017

079720 December 13, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001810-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
